oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry - Royal Barry-Carter Mills - 1953-01-10 - Part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part 2 of Royal, Barry-Carter Mills sponsored Grand Ole Opry show from January 10, 1953. Hosted by Carl Smith.
